high_descs: Turn left and walk to the table.
Pick up the silver knife from the table that is touching the yellow handled knife.
Turn right and walk to the wall then turn right and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the knife in the wine glass.
Pick up the wine glass from inside the fridge and close the door.
Turn right and walk until level with the sink then turn right to face the table.
Put the glass on the table to the left of the apple and wine bottle.
anns.task_desc: Put a cool wine glass with a knife inside it on the table.

high_descs: Move forward, then turn left to face the green table.
Pick up the butter knife on the green table, to the right of the lettuce.
Turn right and go to the wall, then turn right to face the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the butter knife inside of the glass in the fridge.
Pick up the glass from inside the fridge.
Go to the green table behind you.
Put the glass on the green table.
anns.task_desc: Put a glass with a butter knife in it on the table.

high_descs: Look down, walk forward two steps then turn to your left and walk up to the table.
Grab the knife in the very back between the lettuce and egg.
Turn to your right, walk forward three steps then turn right again and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the knife on the wine glass in the back.
Grab the wine glass with the knife in it, then close the fridge.
Turn right then walk forward four steps then turn right again then walk forward to the table.
Place the wine glass on the table on the left side of the apple.
anns.task_desc: Put the knife in the wine glass and set that glass on the table.
